data.description: The perfect home for your family awaits. Walk in to wood floors, a wood burning fireplace and an abundance of natural light. The kitchen has a farm house sink with quartz countertops and an oversized walk in pantry/utility room. Spacious bedrooms and high ceilings throughout this home. Fenced in back yard perfect for entertaining. Conveniently located close to shopping, schools, dining and much more.   ADT Security System is leased and can be transferred to new owner. Please see offer instructions and additional docs.
